# Data Dictionary — Austin Plan Review Cases

**Source:** City of Austin Open Data Portal  
**Dataset:** Plan Review Cases  
**Last Updated:** April 14, 2026  
**Records:** ~178,750 raw / ~156,660 after deduplication  

---

## Raw Fields

| Field | Description | Data Type | Constraints |
|---|---|---|---|
| Case_Type | Type of case (e.g. "Plan Review") | String | Not null |
| Folder_Type | Folder code (e.g. "PR") | String | |
| Sub_Type | Sub-category of permit work | String | |
| Work_Class | Class of work: New, Remodel, Repair | String | |
| Permit_Number | Unique permit identifier | String | Not null, unique |
| Project_Name | Name or address of the project | String | |
| Folder_Description | Free-text description of the work | String | |
| Status_Current | Current permit status (Expired, Issued, etc.) | String | |
| Status_Date | Date of last status change | DateTime | |
| Applied_Date | Date the application was submitted | DateTime | |
| Issued_Date | Date the permit was issued | DateTime | |
| Expires_Date | Date the permit expires | DateTime | |
| Final_Date | Date of final inspection | DateTime | |
| Building_Valuation | Dollar value of building work | Float | >= 0 |
| Electrical_Valuation | Dollar value of electrical work | Float | >= 0 |
| Mechanical_Valuation | Dollar value of mechanical work | Float | >= 0 |
| Plumbing_Valuation | Dollar value of plumbing work | Float | >= 0 |
| Total_Job_Valuation | Total dollar value of the job | Float | >= 0 |
| Number_Of_Units | Number of units in the project | Float | >= 0 |
| Number_Of_Floors | Number of floors in the structure | Float | >= 0 |
| Council_District | Austin city council district | Integer | 1–10 |
| Condominium | Whether property is a condo | String | Yes / No |
| Appraisal_Id | County appraisal district ID | String | |
| Legal_Description | Legal property description | String | |
| Location | GPS coordinates in WKT format | String | POINT (lon lat) |
| Update_Date | Timestamp of last record update | DateTime | ISO 8601 |

---

## Derived Fields (added during transformation)

| Field | Description | Data Type | Source |
|---|---|---|---|
| applied_year | Year of application | Integer | Extracted from Applied_Date |
| applied_quarter | Quarter of application (1–4) | Integer | Extracted from Applied_Date |
| applied_month | Month of application (1–12) | Integer | Extracted from Applied_Date |
| applied_day | Day of application (1–31) | Integer | Extracted from Applied_Date |
| latitude | GPS latitude of property | Float | Extracted from Location |
| longitude | GPS longitude of property | Float | Extracted from Location |
| valid_district | Whether district is valid (1–10) | Boolean | Validated from Council_District |
| ingestion_date | Date data was pulled | Date | Added at ingestion |
